# Serialization

Single path: `src/data-model/serialization.ts` → **SerializedGraphFile** (`format`, `formatVersion: "2.0"`, `graph`, optional `audioSetup`). Extend types there; no parallel save/load format.

Pipeline: deserialize → migrate legacy → **`validateGraph`** → compiler/runtime — no “trusted” graphs without validation.

**Refs:** `serialization.ts`, `validation.ts`, `.cursor/rules/domain/presets.mdc`, `docs/projects/core-architecture/_OVERVIEW.md` (§03A).
